{"tid":1305732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［次緊急］粉嶺連儂牆被塗黑！","createTime":"2019-07-11T02:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T01:12:55.000Z","uid":145126,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"50c5f6a76dff6b8b42fa7b33431c561e943c629b","tid":1305732,"uid":145126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"主旨：我認為粉嶺連儂牆需要人手幫忙用memo紙遮返住啲污跡。<br />\n<br />\n過撚份！呢幾日見到其他區咁多廢老搞事，粉嶺呢個所謂嘅「藍絲重地」幅連儂牆竟然冇事，我都好出奇。<br />\n點知今朝出火車站嘅時候先發現俾人噴黑咗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最仆街連「DSE考生打氣區」都唔放過！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請各位巴絲增援，或者廣傳：如果有貼過memo紙上粉嶺連儂牆嘅話，請再次停下，寫多一張memo紙遮返啲污跡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我眼見一位巴打晚晚留守連儂牆，難道大家忍心俾我哋嘅連儂牆蒙羞？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhVgAvf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhVgAvf.png&h=164beb6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Hew8Qi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Hew8Qi.png&h=cb9645ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFxnv3F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFxnv3F.png&h=8538574c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pA7e6B2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpA7e6B2.png&h=b1042fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w0rb8Qo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw0rb8Qo.png&h=77f75d10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0EXuVvu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0EXuVvu.png&h=4556db2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LL3enay.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLL3enay.png&h=1145075b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g5nuVvB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg5nuVvB.png&h=c9780f74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4uL4KoZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4uL4KoZ.png&h=b13e273d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tb2uVvH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftb2uVvH.png&h=0fe32caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知有冇其他巴絲開咗有關嘅po，無奈我呢刻太憤怒，所以我要開咗先，如果我個po repeat咗其他po嘅話，我在此就洗咗大家版致歉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b34728724c31f291652ecf851df0bbb7a04913","tid":1305732,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d948c627c6788670879f6a104772cea4eb40530","tid":1305732,"uid":182774,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9cb63ae15e65d9c1afbe52074f93229f5ee2ac71","tid":1305732,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d948c627c6788670879f6a104772cea4eb40530","tid":1305732,"uid":182774,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:52:27.000Z","msg":"推 真心"},{"pid":"3db36c9ee47a54cd0a47eee215c536f6b155c80f","tid":1305732,"uid":145126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d948c627c6788670879f6a104772cea4eb40530","tid":1305732,"uid":182774,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:57:22.000Z","msg":"真係由得佢哋咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1ad47139627d4088c172aa3d2f207d0c2c4a94","tid":1305732,"uid":136785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3db36c9ee47a54cd0a47eee215c536f6b155c80f","tid":1305732,"uid":145126,"like":0,"disl