"},{"pid":"a60c1e4c307101ce29032c26b48744fd964c4fba","tid":1305732,"uid":67491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"牛頭角都有人破壞緊"},{"pid":"24541aa2325bcdcd6adbfa1ba7d6db78d25ee26d","tid":1305732,"uid":145126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a60c1e4c307101ce29032c26b48744fd964c4fba","tid":1305732,"uid":67491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"牛頭角都有人破壞緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"頭先石硤尾站連儂場有廢老搞事<br />\n<br />\n我見到有人鬧走咗佢<br />\n<br />\n利申：有幫口"},{"pid":"8821ed058fee93079de63fcb320e0f76a713b078","tid":1305732,"uid":145126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:32:47.000Z","msg":"Update一下大家<br />\n<br />\n我尋晚12點零鐘返到去，見到明顯多咗memo紙，真係好多謝各位香港人。我都有寫返張先走，不過我見到地下有啲memo紙吹跌咗，想呼籲下大家見到連儂牆周圍有垃圾或者吹跌咗嘅memo紙，可以幫手執一執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人好波<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P1YaWik.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP1YaWik.png&h=c3c67cb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n訴求已經延伸到天橋外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCVAnYm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCVAnYm.png&h=c2caca7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日15:30 北方有難，八方增援<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U2L1iwH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU2L1iwH.png&h=736b7701&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fDrsd43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfDrsd43.png&h=2e2ac9b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人貼上「你噴黑佢係冇用㗎」字句<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cdr4gio.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCdr4gio.png&h=41436330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉嶺連儂牆文具經已回歸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ye9dT44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYe9dT44.png&h=198ae212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人寫上「you can&rsquo;t kill us all」字句<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qq040K5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQq040K5.png&h=80c67f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRvpgiq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRvpgiq.png&h=086871c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之見到有人搞破壞，行上次警告佢會犯刑毀，夠姜call食環（呢招建議有小販喺附近先用）。"},{"pid":"79bcaddebb079c71277d2d7583c74dddf2f14c30","tid":1305732,"uid":145126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:04:59.000Z","msg":"輕輕推一推"},{"pid":"ec9c01ca3d70bd39aa95bfdee49ed607e5490240","tid":1305732,"uid":145126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:12:55.000Z","msg":"為咗唔好洗人版，我都係喺度繼續po算喇<br />\n<br />\n星期日凌晨4點左右，facebook page「粉嶺」指粉嶺連儂牆被縱火焚燒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HBSWeDL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHBSWeDL.png&h=57f07b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n截至今日上午九點，連儂牆不見火光，只見一整塊帆布已被清走，地上留下燒焦嘅灰塵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSMjWS1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSMjWS1.png&h=30b40953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLRv3ye.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLRv3ye.png&h=b3d4f8f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一名和理非，我強烈譴責如此暴行，絕不支持網友搜出縱火人士，並不支持任何報復行為。<br />\n<br />\n野火燒不盡 春風吹又生"}]}